OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fcontinue into the evening, some
OL,7,Flocally heavy, but it will become
OL,8,Fincreasingly dry towards midnight,
OL,9,Fwith clear spells developing
OL,10,Fovernight. Cloud will increase across
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland towards dawn.
OL,12,FGenerally staying on the mild side.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FCloud and rain across
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland will spread eastwards
OL,16,Finto Scotland during the day, with
OL,17,Fincreasingly gusty winds developing.
OL,18,FElsewhere, it will be largely dry,
OL,19,Fwith variable amounts of cloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
